00:10:51,865 --> 00:10:54,869
Shalom. So very nice to meet you.

261
00:10:55,393 --> 00:10:56,856
Petra, is it?

262
00:10:58,716 --> 00:11:00,483
<i>Let the good times roll.</i>

263
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:05,424
