00:18:14,312 --> 00:18:16,682
I mean,
I'm taking out the central theme,

402
00:18:16,715 --> 00:18:19,297
so not much makes sense in the
book anymore, but, you know...

403
00:18:19,752 --> 00:18:21,020
I'm sorry, hon.

