00:18:23,297 --> 00:18:25,866
I was already struggling
with notes from my agent.

406
00:18:26,337 --> 00:18:27,972
Didn't know I was gonna have to deal

407
00:18:28,006 --> 00:18:29,442
with notes from my<i> abuela,</i> too.

